            <h1 lang="en" class="lang-content text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">POSTER 24: PROBLEMS ON JOINT WORK</h1>
            <h1 lang="ru" class="lang-content text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">ПЛАКАТ 24: ЗАДАЧИ НА СОВМЕСТНУЮ РАБОТУ</h1>

            <p lang="kk" class="lang-content mt-2 text-xl font-medium text-gray-100">Жұмыс өнімділігі, уақыт және көлем.</p>
            <p lang="en" class="lang-content mt-2 text-xl font-medium text-gray-100">Rate, Time, and Work.</p>
