        <!-- 1. НЕГІЗГІ ФОРМУЛА -->
        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 lang="kk" class="lang-content text-3xl section-heading">1. Негізгі формула</h2>
            <h2 lang="en" class="lang-content text-3xl section-heading">1. The Core Formula</h2>
            <h2 lang="ru" class="lang-content text-3xl section-heading">1. Основная формула</h2>

            <div class="rule-card border-t-emerald-500">
                <div class="text-center p-4 bg-green-50 rounded-lg">
                    <p lang="kk" class="lang-content text-xl font-bold text-green-800"><span class="term" lang="kk">Жұмыс</span> = <span class="term" lang="kk">Өнімділік</span> × <span class="term" lang="kk">Уақыт</span></p>
                    <p lang="en" class="lang-content text-xl font-bold text-green-800"><span class="term" lang="en">Work</span> = <span class="term" lang="en">Rate</span> × <span class="term" lang="en">Time</span></p>
                    <p lang="ru" class="lang-content text-xl font-bold text-green-800"><span class="term" lang="ru">Работа</span> = <span class="term" lang="ru">Производительность</span> × <span class="term" lang="ru">Время</span></p>
                    <p class="mono text-2xl mt-2">A = P × t</p>
                </div>

                <ul class="feature-list text-base text-gray-700 mt-4">
                    <li lang="kk" class="lang-content"><span class="mono">A</span> – Жалпы жұмыс көлемі (мысалы, 1 үй, 1 бассейн, 1 егістік).</li>
                    <li lang="en" class="lang-content"><span class="mono">A</span> – The total Amount of Work (e.g., 1 house, 1 pool, 1 field).</li>
                    <li lang="ru" class="lang-content"><span class="mono">A</span> – Общий объем Работы (напр., 1 дом, 1 бассейн, 1 поле).</li>

                    <li lang="kk" class="lang-content"><span class="mono">P</span> – Өнімділік (уақыт бірлігіндегі жұмыс: 1 сағатта жұмыстың қандай бөлігі бітеді).</li>
                    <li lang="en" class="lang-content"><span class="mono">P</span> (or r) – Rate of work (how much work is done per unit of time, e.g., per hour).</li>
                    <li lang="ru" class="lang-content"><span class="mono">P</span> – Производительность (какая часть работы выполняется за единицу времени, напр., за 1 час).</li>

                    <li lang="kk" class="lang-content"><span class="mono">t</span> – Орындауға кеткен уақыт (сағат, күн).</li>
                    <li lang="en" class="lang-content"><span class="mono">t</span> – Time taken to complete the work (hours, days).</li>
                    <li lang="ru" class="lang-content"><span class="mono">t</span> – Время выполнения работы (часы, дни).</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 2. БІРЛЕСКЕН ЖҰМЫС ЕРЕЖЕСІ -->
        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 lang="kk" class="lang-content text-3xl section-heading">2. Бірлескен жұмыс ережесі</h2>
            <h2 lang="en" class="lang-content text-3xl section-heading">2. Rule of Joint Work</h2>
            <h2 lang="ru" class="lang-content text-3xl section-heading">2. Правило совместной работы</h2>

            <div class="rule-card border-t-green-600">
                <p lang="kk" class="lang-content text-base md:text-lg mb-3 text-gray-700">
                    Екі немесе одан да көп адам/құрал бірге жұмыс істегенде, олардың <span class="term" lang="kk">өнімділіктері (жылдамдықтары) қосылады</span>.
                </p>
                <p lang="en" class="lang-content text-base md:text-lg mb-3 text-gray-700">
                    When two or more people/tools work together, their individual <span class="term" lang="en">rates (speeds) are added</span>.
                </p>
                <p lang="ru" class="lang-content text-base md:text-lg mb-3 text-gray-700">
                    При совместной работе их <span class="term" lang="ru">производительности (скорости) складываются</span>.
                </p>

                <div class="example-block border-l-green-400 text-center">
                    <p class="mono text-2xl">P<span class="term">ортақ</span> = P₁ + P₂</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 3. ЕСЕПТІ ШЫҒАРУ АЛГОРИТМІ -->
        <section class="mb-12">
            <h2 lang="kk" class="lang-content text-3xl section-heading">3. СХЕМА: Есепті шығару алгоритмі</h2>
            <h2 lang="en" class="lang-content text-3xl section-heading">3. SCHEMA: Problem-Solving Algorithm</h2>
            <h2 lang="ru" class="lang-content text-3xl section-heading">3. СХЕМА: Алгоритм решения задачи</h2>

            <div class="rule-card border-t-cyan-500">
                <div class="example-block border-l-cyan-400">
                    <p lang="kk" class="lang-content font-semibold">Есеп:</p>
                    <p lang="en" class="lang-content font-semibold">Problem:</p>
                    <p lang="ru" class="lang-content font-semibold">Задача:</p>

                    <p lang="kk" class="lang-content italic">1-ші трактор егістікті 6 сағатта, ал 2-ші трактор 3 сағатта жыртады. Екі трактор бірге жұмыс істесе, егістікті қанша уақытта жыртып бітіреді?</p>
                    <p lang="en" class="lang-content italic">Tractor 1 can plow a field in 6 hours. Tractor 2 can do it in 3 hours. How long will it take if they work together?</p>
                    <p lang="ru" class="lang-content italic">1-й трактор вспахивает поле за 6 часов, а 2-й – за 3 часа. За сколько часов они вспашут поле, работая вместе?</p>
                </div>

                <div class="example-block border-l-green-400 mt-4">
                    <p lang="kk" class="lang-content font-semibold">Шешуі:</p>
                    <p lang="en" class="lang-content font-semibold">Solution:</p>
                    <p lang="ru" class="lang-content font-semibold">Решение:</p>

                    <ol class="list-decimal list-inside text-gray-700 mt-2 space-y-2">
                        <li lang="kk" class="lang-content">Барлық жұмысты (1 егістік) <span class="mono">A = 1</span> деп аламыз.</li>
                        <li lang="en" class="lang-content">Assume the total work (1 field) is <span class="mono">A = 1</span>.</li>
                        <li lang="ru" class="lang-content">Примем всю работу (1 поле) за <span class="mono">A = 1</span>.</li>

                        <li lang="kk" class="lang-content">1-ші трактордың өнімділігін табамыз: P₁ = 1/t₁ = <span class="mono"><span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>6</span></span></span> (жұмыстың/сағ)</li>
                        <li lang="en" class="lang-content">Find the rate of Tractor 1: P₁ = 1/t₁ = <span class="mono"><span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>6</span></span></span> (of the field/hour)</li>
                        <li lang="ru" class="lang-content">Найдем производительность 1-го: P₁ = 1/t₁ = <span class="mono"><span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>6</span></span></span> (поля/час)</li>

                        <li lang="kk" class="lang-content">2-ші трактордың өнімділігін табамыз: P₂ = 1/t₂ = <span class="mono"><span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>3</span></span></span> (жұмыстың/сағ)</li>
                        <li lang="en" class="lang-content">Find the rate of Tractor 2: P₂ = 1/t₂ = <span class="mono"><span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>3</span></span></span> (of the field/hour)</li>
                        <li lang="ru" class="lang-content">Найдем производительность 2-го: P₂ = 1/t₂ = <span class="mono"><span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>3</span></span></span> (поля/час)</li>

                        <li lang="kk" class="lang-content">Ортақ өнімділікті табамыз (P<span class="term">ортақ</span> = P₁ + P₂):<br><span class="mono ml-5"><span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>6</span></span> + <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>3</span></span> = <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>6</span></span> + <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">2</span><span>6</span></span> = <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">3</span><span>6</span></span> = <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>2</span></span></span></li>
                        <li lang="en" class="lang-content">Find the combined rate (P<span class="term">total</span> = P₁ + P₂):<br><span class="mono ml-5"><span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>6</span></span> + <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>3</span></span> = <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>6</span></span> + <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">2</span><span>6</span></span> = <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">3</span><span>6</span></span> = <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>2</span></span></span></li>
                        <li lang="ru" class="lang-content">Найдем общую производительность (P<span class="term">общ</span> = P₁ + P₂):<br><span class="mono ml-5"><span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>6</span></span> + <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>3</span></span> = <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>6</span></span> + <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">2</span><span>6</span></span> = <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">3</span><span>6</span></span> = <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>2</span></span></span></li>

                        <li lang="kk" class="lang-content">Ортақ уақытты табамыз (t = A / P<span class="term">ортақ</span>):<br><span class="mono ml-5">t = 1 ÷ <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>2</span></span> = 1 × <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">2</span><span>1</span></span> = <strong>2 сағат</strong></span></li>
                        <li lang="en" class="lang-content">Find the total time (t = A / P<span class="term">total</span>):<br><span class="mono ml-5">t = 1 ÷ <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>2</span></span> = 1 × <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">2</span><span>1</span></span> = <strong>2 hours</strong></span></li>
                        <li lang="ru" class="lang-content">Найдем общее время (t = A / P<span class="term">общ</span>):<br><span class="mono ml-5">t = 1 : <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">1</span><span>2</span></span> = 1 × <span class="fraction"><span class="numerator">2</span><span>1</span></span> = <strong>2 часа</strong></span></li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>


        <!-- ТҮЙІН -->
        <footer class="footer-card">
            <h3 lang="kk" class="lang-content text-xl font-extrabold mb-2 text-gray-800">БАСТЫ ОЙ</h3>
            <h3 lang="en" class="lang-content text-xl font-extrabold mb-2 text-gray-800">SUMMARY</h3>
            <h3 lang="ru" class="lang-content text-xl font-extrabold mb-2 text-gray-800">ГЛАВНАЯ МЫСЛЬ</h3>

            <p lang="kk" class="lang-content text-md font-semibold leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
                Барлық жұмысты <span class="term" lang="kk">1</span> деп алыңыз. Әрқайсысының <span class="term" lang="kk">өнімділігін</span> (1/t) табыңыз. Өнімділіктерді <span class="term" lang="kk">қосыңыз</span>. Жалпы уақытты табу үшін 1-ді осы қосындыға <span class="term" lang="kk">бөліңіз</span>.
            </p>
            <p lang="en" class.lang-content="text-md font-semibold leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
                Set the total work to <span class="term" lang="en">1</span>. Find the <span class="term" lang="en">rate</span> (1/t) for each. <span class="term" lang="en">Add</span> the rates. To find the total time, <span class="term" lang="en">divide</span> 1 by that sum.
            </p>
            <p lang="ru" class="lang-content text-md font-semibold leading-relaxed text-gray-700">
                Примите всю работу за <span class="term" lang="ru">1</span>. Найдите <span class="term" lang="ru">производительность</span> (1/t) каждого. <span class="term" lang="ru">Сложите</span> производительности. Чтобы найти общее время, <span class="term" lang="ru">разделите</span> 1 на эту сумму.
            </p>
        </footer>

